**Atal Pension Yojana (APY)** is a government-backed pension scheme for workers in the unorganised sector. You contribute a small monthly amount (based on your age when joining) and receive a guaranteed monthly pension of ₹1,000 to ₹5,000 from age 60. The government co-contributes 50% of your contribution (up to ₹1,000/year) for eligible subscribers.
